re\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russia's Prosecutor General's Office has designated The Moscow Times as an \\\"undesirable\\\" organization, criminalizing our work and putting our staff at risk of prosecution.\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2653, \"end\": 2659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 4.1311654687347865e-12, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 2662, \"end\": 2680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999997489713084, \"rank\": 2.510288337869115e-07, \"text\": \"Prosecutor General\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 2705, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This follows our earlier unjust labeling as a \\\"foreign agent.\\\"\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These actions are direct attempts to silence independent journalism in Russia.\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 4.1311654687347865e-12, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The authorities claim our work \\\"discredits the decisions of the Russian leadership.\\\"\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3032, \"end\": 3039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"score\": 0.9999998502587572, \"rank\": 1.4456502087176593e-07, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We see things differently: we strive to provide accurate, unbiased reporting on Russia.\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 4.1311654687347865e-12, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We, the journalists of The Moscow Times, refuse to be silenced.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3165, \"end\": 3181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But to continue our work,we need your help.\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your support, no matter how small, makes a world of difference.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you can, please support us monthly starting from just$2.It's quick to set up, and every contribution makes a significant impact.\", \"from\": 3315, \"to\": 3446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By supporting The Moscow Times, you are defending open, independent journalism in the face of repression.\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3462, \"end\": 3478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for standing with us.\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3585, \"entities\": []}]}"